text: Georgy Nikitin (born 26 April 1973) is a Russian rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Russia Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
